---
title: Apricot Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Potatoes and Spring Salad
description: The combination of apricot jam and mustard makes a summary and delicious glaze for pork in the middle of the winter! Roasted potatoes and a bright spring-inspired salad add richness and texture, making every mouthful an experience in taste.
